lead_paragraph: Susannah Aboff, a Princeton University junior, added a four-under-par 68 to her opening-round score of 72 to win the 20th Annual Lincoln Women’s Met Open Championship at Ridgewood Country Club yesterday. Aboff of Huntington Country Club became the fourth amateur to win the event. Her round included one bogey, on the par-5 17th hole, along with five birdies.
